Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Tompkins Square Park Riot (1988)
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yh5k1
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 31 May 1991
The social injustice which sparked riots in Tompkins Square Park in 1988, and how the social acceptibilty of homelessness has changed over the years.